    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《机器人狂怒》是一款机甲战斗模拟器，让你感受到真正的机器人战士的快感。用强大的火焰喷射器与敌人作战，带着喷气背包飞向战斗，用精准的机枪爆头击败敌人。自定义你的机甲，参与激烈的史诗级战斗！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/1ea5d7a710efbdb47c97d2ffd9c33bc5.webp?t=1772360513\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/6b7ce86429df7ff55dfa459f948e7414.poster.avif?t=1772360513\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/6b7ce86429df7ff55dfa459f948e7414.webm?t=1772360513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/6b7ce86429df7ff55dfa459f948e7414.mp4?t=1772360513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于《机器人狂怒》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《机器人狂怒》是一款激动人心的机甲战斗模拟器，将你带入强大、可自定义的机甲驾驶舱。体验机械化战争的刺激，使用火焰喷射器、机枪和火箭发射器与敌人激战。借助喷气背包飞入战场，执行精准攻击来击败敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/9f20e7601dbf18ea95490c990242faa1.webp?t=1772360513\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/422693eae6753cf8e4371ca8e640f3ca.poster.avif?t=1772360513\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/422693eae6753cf8e4371ca8e640f3ca.webm?t=1772360513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234450/extras/422693eae6753cf8e4371ca8e640f3ca.mp4?t=1772360513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供多种任务和挑战，让你测试战斗技巧和战术决策。根据自己的游戏风格自定义机甲，升级武器，并调整能力以应对不同威胁。通过激烈的战斗场景和动态环境，《机器人狂怒》为玩家提供了一个紧张刺激、身临其境的体验，每一场战斗都是证明自己作为顶级机甲驾驶员的机会！</p>",
